514
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:19,000
or has just disappeared.

515
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,000
However you look at it,

516
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,000
it doesn't matter.

517
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,000
There's the merging.

518
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:24,000
The merging is even extra.

519
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:27,000
There's the realization that there never was a separation.

520
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:34,000
And in each aspect of those eight stages of,

521
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:36,000
eight gates of practice,

522
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:39,000
that same thing is functioning.

523
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:41,000
Non-dual.

524
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:44,000
So in the face-to-face teaching,

525
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:47,000
no separation is at the heart of it.

526
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:54,000
In our academic study,

527
